{"version":3,"kind":"Notebook","sha256":"14a613e6c327818b0d3e4e5d7826aad30de3b91bd9935f0ae99d53b1bff42004","slug":"road-comparison","location":"/content/road_comparison.ipynb","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Straßen Vergleich","content_includes_title":false,"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3 (ipykernel)","language":"python"},"numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"thumbnail":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/road_comparison_peru-19e1310a6ade4567422dd6ad45233782.png","exports":[{"format":"ipynb","filename":"road_comparison.ipynb","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/road_comparison-dc0d90d5e394a50b0958d3ec12dbc509.ipynb"}]},"widgets":{},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-content","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der Road Comparison Indicator schätzt die Vollständigkeit der OSM-Straßendaten anhand eines Referenzdatensatzes. Das Ergebnis ist ein Verhältnis der Länge der Referenzstraßen, die durch OSM-Straßen abgedeckt sind, zur Gesamtlänge des Referenzdatensatzes.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"key":"qZPac8FbNs"}],"key":"QgQq6KhIwt"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Methoden und Daten","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"ZRosYxmaiY"}],"identifier":"methoden-und-daten","label":"Methoden und Daten","html_id":"methoden-und-daten","implicit":true,"key":"Xeu8NIa2IO"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-> Extrinsische Methode","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"rErvpCiZnu"}],"key":"oxcfnjPe31"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der Indikator identifiziert entsprechende Straßengeometrien in OSM und im Referenzdatensatz, um das Verhältnis der übereinstimmenden Straßenlänge in km zu berechnen.\nDer Microsoft Roads Datensatz wird als Referenz verwendet. Allerdings sollte der Referenzdatensatz nicht als vollständig korrekt und aktuell betrachtet werden.\nDer Road Comparison Indicator ist nur für das Feature „cars (all highway)“ verfügbar.","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"oQ8lENot7r"}],"key":"cEglFaF4nj"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Referenzdatensatz:","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"z3MA8WKvte"}],"key":"x5vpXWnjEI"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"link","url":"https://github.com/microsoft/RoadDetections","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Microsoft Roads","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"I0V49zUksS"}],"urlSource":"https://github.com/microsoft/RoadDetections","error":true,"key":"NI078xn0MH"},{"type":"text","value":": Der Microsoft Roads Datensatz ist ein weltweiter Straßendatensatz. Ein Machine-Learning-Ansatz wurde verwendet, um Straßen aus Satellitenbildern abzuleiten.","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"h8BO9KxpqX"}],"key":"lwmqk8FW3o"}],"key":"ma8GuQAFkm"}],"key":"KnEypzgeio"},{"type":"image","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/road_comparison_peru-19e1310a6ade4567422dd6ad45233782.png","alt":"road_comparison","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column